{
  "stem": "12462.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me of some underground people that had managed to survive in-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got to Nuremberg, I already knew some anti-Nazi Germans who I was going to interrogate and make friends with and get affidavits from and so forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the early affidavits I got from these oppositionists to the Nazi regime were all introduced in evidence, and not a one of them was ever questioned or any cross-examination done.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The evidence stood 100%.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, you mention that because of your discovery of the Norwegian plan documents, you came to the attention of Justice Jackson.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When did you first meet Justice Jackson?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In London in-- in June of 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'd-- somebody in London said this fellow's discovered some documents and said he'd better come back here and check in with some more other-- some other people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I came back, and I came in to London and got to know a few of the people on the staff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of them immediately said, we want to introduce you to Justice Jackson, and he's seen some of the documents you found and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I met him, had a brief interview with him, or he questioned me a little bit and said, go back to Paris and find some more documents like this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was my introduction to Justice Jackson.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was one of the first two officers to-- to be permanently assigned to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "August 20, 1945, I flew into Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lieutenant Colonel William H.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Baldwin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he had gone in several days ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the second officer to be assigned in permanently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I was first lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first task I had in Nuremberg may interest you.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
